  {"file": "0.bin", "record": "0x8F54", "zh": "哼……"},
  {"file": "0.bin", "record": "0x8F64", "zh": "不想死就归顺我们……饶你不死"},
  {"file": "0.bin", "record": "0x8F90", "zh": "不可能……"},
  {"file": "0.bin", "record": "0x8FA8", "zh": "休想挡我野望！！"},
